title: Coal Mine Entrances, Iowa, 2003
name: Coal Mine Entrances, Iowa, 2003
description:
Abstract:
    Point coverage of underground mine entrances digitized from surveyed coal mine maps, identified by type of entrance. 
Purpose:
    This digital, geographically referenced data set was developed by the Iowa Department of Natural Resources to carry out agency responsibilities related to management, protection, and development of Iowa's natural resources. 
Supplemental_Information:
    This file was constructed for the purpose of queries and plotting.
